message.body: Happy birthday, you verdant swamp of a beautiful man.
You always remember! Thank you, you prolapsed pearlescent arachnid of pious joy.
Or buttery cheeked baby of lucifer.
Either way you are beautiful imagery in my blackened heart.
Sweet Pearlescent dome of pallid fluorescent light briefly shown in my most dark and susceptible chasms. Your buzzes and flickers rouse me, sweet generous poison oak.
Youre much better at this than i am.
Your the best at everything else then.
Ha ha. Ive gotta sign off and finish this syllabus. But i am glad to hear from you and lets talk soon.
Sure, always good to talk to you buddy.
